{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do I have to introduce myself?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just wanted to add a few things about Laura, who was not only my-- I mean, she was my foster mother, but she had about 30 children under her wing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very hard for us in the beginning, because we were all very artistic in this room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were room 25 at a house that was called L 410 in-- in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came-- I mean, Laura came and wanted us to be clean and orderly and straighten our beds, and have some kind of normalcy instead of going just to sing and act and write and whatever children would prefer to do.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was quite a hard time for all of us, but I think it was very important that she put some order and discipline into our life, because it is also a semblance of normalcy that was completely missing there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, this is one thing that I can never understand, because everybody asks me this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, look, when I was 12 or 13 years old, anybody five years older is old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, grown up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was probably a very young woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was probably-- she was a young woman, I guess, and she had-- yes, she was very leftish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was, of course, Jewish, but very, like, for justice and all this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, there were two main streams in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the Zionists and the communists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But today to say communist is almost like-- you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, it was like somebody who was idealistic, and anybody who wasn't wasn't like idealistic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So its terminology is very bad, but she was a very orderly person.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
